---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Vaccine Safety Signals">
  <article class="prose-page">
    <h1>About this site</h1>
    <p>This is an independent, evidence-first presentation of the U.S. Senate Permanent Subcommittee on Investigations' April 29, 2026 majority-staff interim report <em>Unmasked: How Biden Health Officials Purposely Turned a Blind Eye Toward COVID-19 Vaccine Safety Signals</em>, together with the Bates-stamped HHS records, witness testimony, and other exhibits the Subcommittee published with it.</p>
    <p>The site is not affiliated with the Subcommittee. Its purpose is to make the underlying records — emails, presentations, FOIA productions, journal papers — accessible and navigable to readers without a pharmacovigilance background, and to honestly disclose where the cited record is or is not publicly available.</p>
    <h2>Methodology</h2>
    <p>Source documents are downloaded from the Subcommittee's hearing page, and OCR'd with <code>ocrmypdf</code>. ("OCR" means Optical Character Recognition.) Citations in the report are extracted by Bates ID and cross-referenced against the document catalog.</p>
    <h2>From the author</h2>
    <p>This website was created by Marjorie Roswell. I will not forget the day Dr. Peter Marks told a roomful of bereaved and vaccine-injured people that there were no signals in FDA data suggesting any relationship between the COVID-19 vaccines and the losses and conditions we had endured. The records the Subcommittee has now made public — and which this site presents — show that FDA's safety data mining had in fact been masking signals (yielding missed signals) when those reassurances were given.</p>

    <p>Furthermore, he had been <strong>told</strong> by experts how to <strong>not</strong> mask the signals. He had chosen not to implement the fix.</p>

    <p>There is a human impact, which in some cases is devastating.</p>

    <h2>Feedback</h2>
    <p>If you've found something on this site to correct, supplement, or discuss, please use the form below.</p>

    <form
      class="contact-form"
      action="https://formspree.io/f/mwvywkzb"
      method="POST"
    >
      <label class="field">
        <span class="field-label">Name <small>(optional)</small></span>
        <input type="text" name="name" autocomplete="name" />
      </label>

      <label class="field">
        <span class="field-label">Email <small>(only needed if you'd like a reply)</small></span>
        <input type="email" name="email" autocomplete="email" />
      </label>

      <label class="field">
        <span class="field-label">Message</span>
        <textarea name="message" rows="6" required></textarea>
      </label>

      {/* Honeypot — hidden from human users; bots that fill every field
          get caught and discarded by Formspree. */}
      <input type="text" name="_gotcha" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" class="honeypot" aria-hidden="true" />

      {/* Customize the email subject Formspree sends you. */}
      <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="Vaccine Safety Signals — feedback" />

      <button type="submit" class="contact-submit">Send</button>
    </form>

    <p class="form-note">
      Submissions go through <a href="https://formspree.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Formspree</a>; spreadsheet logging is configured in the Formspree dashboard.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .prose-page { max-width: var(--max-prose); margin: 0 auto; }

  .contact-form {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin: 1.25rem 0 0.75rem;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 6px;
  }
  .field { display: grid; gap: 0.35rem; }
  .field-label {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  .field-label small {
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    margin-left: 0.3rem;
  }
  .field input,
  .field textarea {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    padding: 0.55rem 0.7rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: var(--color-bg);
    color: var(--color-text);
    width: 100%;
  }
  .field textarea {
    resize: vertical;
    min-height: 6rem;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .field input:focus,
  .field textarea:focus {
    outline: 2px solid var(--color-accent);
    outline-offset: -2px;
    background: white;
  }
  .honeypot {
    position: absolute;
    left: -10000px;
    top: auto;
    width: 1px;
    height: 1px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .contact-submit {
    justify-self: start;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: white;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 0.55rem 1.2rem;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .contact-submit:hover { filter: brightness(1.08); }
  .form-note {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    margin-top: 0.6rem;
  }
</style>
